    <li>sacrifice(p=4)->[sacrifice_neutral]</li>
    <li>sacrifice(p=2)->[sacrifice_masc]</li>
    <li>sacrifice(p=1)->[sacrifice_fem]</li>
	<li>sacrifice_neutral->действо</li>
	<li>sacrifice_neutral->отмечание</li>
